<PKG>_INSTALL_OPTS
^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^

Provides a means to pass command line options into the installation process.
This option can be defined as a dictionary of string pairs or a list with
strings -- either way defined will generate argument values to include in the
installation event. This field is optional.

.. code-block:: python

   LIBFOO_INSTALL_OPTS = {
       # adds "--option value" to the command
       '--option': 'value',
   }

   # (or)

   LIBFOO_INSTALL_OPTS = [
       # adds "--some-option" to the command
       '--some-option',
   ]
